ES EPROUVES (plus tard) (Voir CS)","id":"CH 26","textes":"</i></p><p>","gamme":"","rythme":"","auteur":""}, {"titre":"27. EE YESU NIOKOWE","id":"CH 27","textes":"</p><p>1.Ee Yesu niokowe, nisianguke<br>matopeni, Wewe ndiye msaada wangu;<br>mwamba wa uzima.</p><p><i>Bwana Yesu - Mwamba wa uzima;</i><br><i>Ndiye Neno - Mwamba wa uzima;</i><br><i>La uzima - Mwamba wa uzima;</i><br><i>Mwamba, mwamba - mwamba wa</i><br><i>uzima.</i></p><p>2.Eh! Yesu uniponye, adui wananizunguka. Wewe ndiye msaada wangu; mwamba wa uzima.</p><p>3.Eh! Yesu nashukuru, Maombi<br>umeyasikia Kwa kunipa neno lako;<br>mwamba wa uzima.</p>","gamme":"","rythme":"","auteur":""}, {"titre":"28. NATAZAMA KWA MBALI","id":"CH 28","textes":"<p>1. Natazama kwa mbali ngambo ya yordani, kuja ku nipeleka nyumbani, kundi la malaika, wanakuja kwangu, kunipeleka nyumbani.</p><p><i>Shuka, gari nzuri, kuja kunipeleka nyumbani x2</i></p><p>2. Ukienda huko kabla sija fika, kuja kunipeleka nyumbani ambia rafiki, ninakuja pia, kunipeleka nyumbani.</p><p>","gamme":"","rythme":"","auteur":""}, {"titre":"29. TON AMOUR NOUS ENVIRON (CS 288)","id":"CH 29","textes":"</p><p>","gamme":"","rythme":"","auteur":""}, {"titre":"30. BWANA NINAKUHITAJI KATI","id":"CH 30","textes":"</p><p>1. Bwana ninakuhitaji katika maisha yangu,uniongoze, Mungu wangu kwa imani nikutumikie. x2</p><p>2. Sina nguvu Mungu wangu ya kushinda majaribu, wewe Yesu unijaze kwa imani nikutumikiye. x2</p><p>3. Maisha yangu yote ni mali ya mwokozi, maungo roho na akili yeye ame ya badilisha. 2x</p><p>Ref: Mwanga wangu, nuru yangu, niwashiye moto wako, :/ :nikutumikie eh Bwana:/:<br>","gamme":"","rythme":"","auteur":""}, {"titre":"31. WAKATI BWANA YESU ALIPOFIKA","id":"CH 31","textes":"</p><p>1. Sop 1 : Wakati Bwana Yesu alipo fika nyumbani mwao rafiki Lazarooo,</p><p>Ts : alimukuta lazaro amekufa</p><p>Sop 1 : wakaondoka hata kaburini, akapatwa na huzuni kubwa</p><p>Ts : hata machozi ikamutoka. x2</p><p><i>Bwana Yesu akaamuru watoe jiwe kwenye kaburi, ndipo ali